In re A.N.B. No. 428PA04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 21, 2005. Charles W. Porter, Charlotte, for Mother.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 13th day of April 2005 by Respondent to Dismiss Appeal and Motion to Strike Brief and Appendix Memorandum of Law:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference this the 21st day of April 2005."
